title: Next Man Up: A Streaming Guide for Week 15 | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Week 14 witnessed a catastrophic slate of injuries across the fantasy landscape. On today’s show we map out how to salvage your team at every position.
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
